description: Refurbishment of existing four storey building and erection of part 10 and part 14 storey building (39m high), including basement to provide 2377sqm gross of class B1 floorspace, 19 live/work units on 2nd and 3rd and 114 residential units, comprising 15 x 1 bed, 93 x 2 bed and 6 x 3 bed flats together with the provision of 43 car parking spaces, 26 scooter parking spaces and 30 bicycle spaces.
